{"tid":2328944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來獵人唔係吸毒，係噴筒畫大師，重就來開畫展","createTime":"2020-12-17T01:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T01:48:03.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad6f584a2cca95fc3bd0cbdb420ece40589ab5f","tid":2328944,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"屌你！真係當人白痴<br />\n===================================<br />\n&bull;Georges Berg&egrave;s Gallery plans to host the solo exhibition next year, sources say<br />\n&bull;Hunter Biden has credited his art with keeping him 'sane' in tough times<br />\n&bull;His work consists of blown-ink abstractions on Japanese Yupo paper<br />\n&bull;He has experience as lawyer and investment advisor, but not professional artist<br />\n&bull;Justice Department is currently probing Hunter's taxes and foreign dealings<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36919078-9058399-Hunter_Biden_pictured_at_work_in_his_art_studio_in_Los_Angeles_i-a-8_1608147973607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36919078-9058399-Hunter_Biden_pictured_at_work_in_his_art_studio_in_Los_Angeles_i-a-8_1608147973607.jpg&h=5510f4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Hunter Biden pictured at work in his art studio in Los Angeles in November, blowing alcohol ink through a metal straw<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36919080-9058399-Hunter_credits_the_creative_endeavor_as_literally_keeping_me_san-a-9_1608147973645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36919080-9058399-Hunter_credits_the_creative_endeavor_as_literally_keeping_me_san-a-9_1608147973645.jpg&h=85080d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Hunter credits the creative endeavor as 'literally keeping me sane' following struggles with crack addiction and scrutiny over his Ukraine business dealings<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36903548-9058399-Georges_Berg_s_Gallery_in_SoHo_is_inking_a_deal_to_represent_Hun-a-10_1608147973647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36903548-9058399-Georges_Berg_s_Gallery_in_SoHo_is_inking_a_deal_to_represent_Hun-a-10_1608147973647.jpg&h=1e7c85f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Georges Berg&egrave;s Gallery in SoHo is inking a deal to represent Hunter Biden, 50, a previously 'unknown' artist who hopes to make a splash with his solo debut<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36929654-9058399-image-a-18_1608148081432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36929654-9058399-image-a-18_1608148081432.jpg&h=f97c595c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A series of compromising pictures of Hunter Biden were released before the presidential election. In some of the images, he is seen with a crack pipe hanging out of his mouth. His struggles with drug addiction have been well documented in the past<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36903554-9058399-A_prior_exhibition_is_seen_at_the_Georges_Berg_s_Gallery_Hunter_-a-11_1608147973649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36903554-9058399-A_prior_exhibition_is_seen_at_the_Georges_Berg_s_Gallery_Hunter_-a-11_1608147973649.jpg&h=a45e2766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A prior exhibition is seen at the Georges Berg&egrave;s Gallery. Hunter's artwork consists of blow-ink decorative abstractions on Japanese Yupo paper<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/12/16/19/36903550-9058399-It_comes_as_the_heat_on_Hunter_s_foreign_deals_increases_with_th-a-12_1608147973650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F19%2F36903550-9058399-It_comes_as_the_heat_on_Hunter_s_foreign_deals_increases_with_th-a-12_1608147973650.jpg&h=88e054f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n It comes as the heat on Hunter's foreign deals increases, with the disclosure of a DOJ probe and rumors of a special counsel. Above, a prior exhibit at Georges Berg&egrave;s is seen<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2020/12/11/1807038441428398132/1024x576_MP4_1807038441428398132.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2020%2F12%2F11%2F1807038441428398132%2F1024x576_MP4_1807038441428398132.mp4&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c62dd378\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2020/12/11/1807038441428398132/1024x576_MP4_1807038441428398132.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9058399/Hunter-Biden-planning-solo-art-Manhattans-ritzy-Georges-Berg-s-Gallery.html#comments\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9058399%2FHunter-Biden-planning-solo-art-Manhattans-ritzy-Georges-Berg-s-Gallery.html%23comments&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c2fcfcb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9058399/Hunter-Biden-planning-solo-art-Manhattans-ritzy-Georges-Berg-s-Gallery.html#comments</a>"},{"pid":"21b263d301273e3aaf54f6da4d381a8abc4496fa","tid":2328944,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f7dde1f9419a00e406705a3b1b5d4fa6f9623a","tid":2328944,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"繼續吹<img s